doctype html

html(lang='en-us')
    head
        meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='IE=Edge')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
        meta(charset='UTF-8')

        title Save, share and collaborate | Blocbox

        link(href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:300,400,700,300italic,400italic,700italic|Varela+Round' rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

        link(href='css/style.css', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')

    body
        // Hero
        header
            nav.container
                .one-half
                    a.site-logo(href='index.html')
                        img(src='images/site-logo.png', alt='Blocbox')
                .one-half
                    ul
                        li
                            a(href='signin.html') Sign In
                        li.btn-outline
                            a(href='signup.html') Sign Up
            .container.hero
                h1 Save, share and collaborate.
                // This next block might benefit from using white-space:pre
                // See: http://stackoverflow.com/a/6752736
                p blocbox lets you collect and sort information.<br/>Create simple notes, store images, and add links.
                a.btn(href='signup.html') Start Your Free Trial!
                img(src='images/dashboard-screenshot.png', alt='Blocbox')

        main(role='main')

            // Benefits
            section.benefits
                ul.container
                    li.one-third
                        i.fa.fa-file-o
                        h2 Create notes
                        p Using Markdown, you can create simple text-based documents to save and share. You can collaborate with others to write and edit content.
                    li.one-third
                        i.fa.fa-picture-o
                        h2 Create notes
                        p Are there images you find interesting enough to save? Now you have a way to organize and store those within blocbox.
                    li.one-third
                        i.fa.fa-link
                        h2 Create notes
                        p Forget bookmarking sites in your browser. With blocbox, you can add links, group them and view them from any computer.

            // Pricing
            section.pricing
              .container
                h2 How much does blocbox cost?
                p
                  | We have many options to fit your needs. It's free to try for 30 days*, and you can always change your plan once you signed up.
                  br
                  | Here are the different features of each plan:
              ul.container
                li.one-third
                  .box
                    h3 Casual
                    h4 Free
                    ul
                      li Up to 5 boxes
                      li Up to 10 collaborators
                      li
                        strong 2GB
                        |  of storage
                    a.btn(href='signup.html') Start Your Free Trial!
                li.one-third
                  .box.middle
                    h3 Professional
                    h4
                      span.currency-mark $
                      | 5
                      span.month /month
                    ul
                      li Unlimited boxes
                      li Up to 20 collaborators
                      li
                        strong 5GB
                        |  of storage
                      li Real-time collaboration
                    a.btn(href='signup.html') Start Your Free Trial!
                li.one-third
                  .box
                    h3 Expert
                    h4
                      span.currency-mark $
                      | 10
                      span.month /month
                    ul
                      li Unlimited boxes
                      li Unlimited collaborators
                      li
                        strong Unlimited
                        |  storage
                      li Real-time collaboration
                    a.btn(href='signup.html') Start Your Free Trial!
              .container
                p.small
                    | *We will not collect your credit card information until your 30-day trial has ended.

